    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 for a Class II device under the documented QA framework. Discretization error, output comparison, and validation relevance factors all demonstrate adequate simulation credibility for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions. The relative hemolysis index acceptance criterion (RH < 1) is satisfied across all 5 operating conditions. The credibility package is accepted for regulatory submission supporting the CPB device tolerance analysis.",
